674
00:36:59,260 --> 00:37:00,530
This is an accident.

675
00:37:07,420 --> 00:37:09,530
Mr. Xiao, eat up. The dishes are getting cold.

676
00:37:12,590 --> 00:37:13,200
Mr. Zhou.

677
00:37:13,690 --> 00:37:14,380
Thank you.

678
00:37:21,100 --> 00:37:23,340
