707
00:39:07,600 --> 00:39:08,210
It doesn’t matter.

708
00:39:10,630 --> 00:39:11,120
You're right.

709
00:39:15,310 --> 00:39:16,530
I won't look at him.

710
00:39:16,790 --> 00:39:17,350
You...

